   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ClearAll[x, p, kx, kp, t1, t2, m, q, \\[HBar], \\[Sigma]x, \\[Sigma]p];\r\n\r\n(* -------------------------------\r\n   Full assumption set (IMPORTANT)\r\n-------------------------------- *)\r\n$Assumptions =\r\n  Element[{x, p, kx, kp, t1, t2, m, q, \\[HBar], \\[Sigma]x, \\[Sigma]p}, Reals] &&\r\n  \\[Sigma]x > 0 && \\[Sigma]p > 0 &&\r\n  m > 0 && q > 0 && t1 > 0 && t2 > 0 && \\[HBar] > 0;\r\n\r\n\r\n(* -------------------------------\r\n   Shifts\r\n-------------------------------- *)\r\nA1 = x - (v+(q1+q2)/2)*(t1+t2)/m + q2*t1/(2*m)\r\nA = q2/\\[HBar]*(x - (v+(q1+q2)/2)*t2/m)\r\nB = q1/\\[HBar]*(x - (v+(q1+q2)/2)*(t1+t2)/m + q2*t1/(2*m))\r\n\r\n\r\nfv2 = (t1+t2)^2/(2*\\[Sigma]x^2*m^2)+1/(2*\\[Sigma]p^2)\r\nfv = (t1+t2)/m*(x+q2*t1/(2*m)-(q1+q2)/2*(t1+t2)/m)/\\[Sigma]x^2\r\nf = (x+q2*t1/(2*m)-(q1+q2)/2*(t1+t2)/m)^2/(2*\\[Sigma]x^2)\r\n\r\nAv = q2/\\[HBar]*(-t2/m)\r\nA = q2/\\[HBar]*(x-(q1+q2)/2*t2/m)\r\n\r\nBv = q1/\\[HBar]*(-(t1+t2)/m)\r\nB = q1/\\[HBar]*(x+q2*t1/(2*m)-(q1+q2)/2*(t1+t2)/m)\r\n\r\n\r\nF = Sqrt[Pi/fv2]*Exp[f]*(Exp[(fv+I*(Av+Bv))^2/(4*fv2)+(A+B)]\r\n                        + Exp[(fv+I*(Av-Bv))^2/(4*fv2)+(A-B)]\r\n                        + Exp[(fv+I*(-Av+Bv))^2/(4*fv2)+(-A+B)]\r\n                        + Exp[(fv+I*(-Av-Bv))^2/(4*fv2)+(-A-B)])",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
