  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ClearAll[X, d, a, b, c];\r\n(* (* X = x + q2*t1/(2*m) - (q1+q2)*(t1+t2)/(2*m);\r\n\r\nd = 1/(2 \\[Sigma]p^2) + (t1+t2)^2/(2 m^2 \\[Sigma]x^2); *)\r\n\r\na = (t1+t2) X/(m \\[Sigma]x^2);\r\n\r\nb = q1 (t1+t2)/(m \\[HBar]);\r\n\r\nc = q2 t2/(m \\[HBar]); *)\r\n\r\nFd = F /. {\r\n ((q2*t1)/(2*m) - ((q1+q2)(t1+t2))/(2*m) + x) -> X,\r\n 1/(2 \\[Sigma]p^2) + (t1+t2)^2/(2 m^2 \\[Sigma]x^2) -> M\r\n}\r\nInputForm[Fd]\r\n\r\nFd /. {(t1+t2) X/(m \\[Sigma]x^2) -> a,\r\n q1 (-t1-t2)/(m \\[HBar]) -> -b,\r\n q2 t2/(m \\[HBar]) -> c,\r\n (q2*(-1/2*((q1 + q2)*t2)/m + x))/\\[HBar] + (q1*X)/\\[HBar] -> d\r\n}\r\n",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wexpr\"><wgraph class=\"resizable\" style=\"width:763px;height:136px;\" aspect-ratio=\"0.1782\" tabIndex=\"-1\"><img class=\"invert-brightness\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" /></wgraph></div>",
